name: Preserve My Love
description:
Does not matter what happens to me I always protect my love.
The truth of heart which is unspoken from words is carried on by this skull artwork. This artwork is so pure it does not have any boundation of gender,  caste, religion, skin color, nationality, and no expectation in return. My love is infinite and never gets into the galaxies of this universe. The faith I have in my love is unmatched and it will never ever happen again.  

Yes I am yours
